description:
Stories in this comic:

  • Tubby the Scout - Where Tubby waits for an accident to happen so he can earn his first-aid badge
  • Nip the Cat in 'Mouser Trouncer' - Where Nip the Cat reads in a book that he should be catching mice
  • There's a Word For It - A two page textual story
  • Leon the Lyin' Lion in Ah-Choo!!! - Where Leon lies his way to a $5 prize
  • Punchy and The Black Crow - Where Shorty sells Bruno and Blackie the same book to give to Punchy who's already bought one for himself
  • Leon the Lyin' Lion - Where Leon and his friends are hounded by aggressive mosquitoes
  • The last few pages contain several half page comic stories with various characters

Stories included are:

  • Pesty the Porcupine Shows a Stunt - two-page short textual story
  • Timmy the Timid Ghost in 'See What You've Done' - Where Timmy plays with his invisible dog
  • Li'l Genius in 'Love at First Sight' - Where Ollie finds his one true love
  • The All American Tom Cat in 'Fish Story' - Where Tom tells a bit of a fib
  • Li'l Tomboy in 'The Hoop Skirt' - Where she almost loses her friends over a hoop skirt
  • Timmy the Timid Ghost in 'Gus the Goofy Li'l Ghost' - Where Gus is the stupid ghost
  • The All American Tom Cat in 'Of Course' - Where Tom plays a little golf
  • Timmy the Timid Ghost in 'Hear This' - Where Timmy thinks he's found someone more timid than himself
  • Li'l Tomboy in 'Next Time Don't Laugh' - Where Tomboy tries to grow some muscle
  • Timmy the Timid Ghost in 'Night at the Museum' - Where Timmy has a nightmare
  • Kiwi the Kee-Weer - two-page textual story
  • Li'l Genius in 'The Gardner' - Where Ollie plants something in the garden
  • Timmy the Timid Ghost in 'The 500th Face' - Where Timmy looks in a mirror
  • Li'l Genius in 'Bless his Little Heart' - Where Ollie gives a man a dime
  • Li'l Genius in 'Happy Birthday' - Where Ollie loses his mom's shirt

All comics are in color
